1
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:08,560
Professor Chu,

2
00:01:09,239 --> 00:01:10,760
why do you bring me here?

3
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:16,840
Have you ever seen the world after death?

4
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:27,319
Don't worry,

5
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:28,840
I'm not that evil.

6
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:30,079
I won't let you die.

7
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:36,879
The world after death may not exist,

8
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:38,920
but I want you to experience

9
00:01:39,879 --> 00:01:41,959
the tranquility of another world

10
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:43,879
and the transparency of

11
00:01:49,319 --> 00:01:50,239
near-death experience.

12
00:01:51,159 --> 00:01:53,760
NDE?

13
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:55,719
People say that

14
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:57,640
once you've died, you'll see everything

15
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:58,640
as it really is.

16
00:01:59,879 --> 00:02:00,719
That's true.

17
00:02:01,879 --> 00:02:04,239
But it's not worth dying for.

18
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:05,959
I saw a report.

19
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:08,599
A psychologist named Kenneth Ring

20
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:11,159
found that even people who are blind

21
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:13,639
since birth

22
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:16,120
can see something

23
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:18,000
in the process of describing the NDE.

24
00:02:19,039 --> 00:02:20,000
That's amazing.

25
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:22,360
So,

26
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,319
what would the world look like

27
00:02:24,319 --> 00:02:25,360
to Lu Qi,

28
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,840
who has

29
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,000
a pair of beautiful eyes?

30
00:02:32,599 --> 00:02:34,400
Then it's a summary of the past

31
00:02:34,479 --> 00:02:35,680
and a release of the present.

32
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,719
When I was studying abroad,

33
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,800
I also came into contact with many NDErs.

34
00:02:41,639 --> 00:02:43,439
Most of them agreed that

35
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:45,840
extreme

36
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,439
sense of peace.

37
00:02:50,639 --> 00:02:50,879
Sit.

38
00:03:00,479 --> 00:03:00,960
Lu Qi,

39
00:03:02,639 --> 00:03:03,479
you're very talented,

40
00:03:06,159 --> 00:03:07,560
but now your soul

41
00:03:08,159 --> 00:03:09,879
is not strong enough to carry it.

42
00:03:14,639 --> 00:03:15,400
If possible,

43
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:17,599
I really hope

44
00:03:17,599 --> 00:03:18,759
you can use this way

45
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:20,360
to find your true self.

46
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,240
No matter how much others say,

47
00:03:22,879 --> 00:03:24,039
it's not as real as your own experience.

48
00:03:24,039 --> 00:03:25,000
It's more real than anything else.

49
00:03:25,719 --> 00:03:27,240
After all, whether a dagger is sharp or not,

50
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:29,599
only when it is stabbed into your body,

51
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,319
can you feel it.

52
00:03:37,919 --> 00:03:39,039
Then

53
00:03:40,319 --> 00:03:42,000
what should we do specifically?

54
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:48,879
Speak.

55
00:03:49,199 --> 00:03:49,800
Master

56
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:51,159
Chumo drove too fast,

57
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:52,719
I lost him in the sea of clouds.

58
00:03:56,439 --> 00:03:57,120
The sea of clouds.

59
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,199
Don't worry.

60
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,759
I won't let you get hurt.

61
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,560
Do you see anything?

62
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,160
I see

63
00:04:27,519 --> 00:04:28,399
a piece

64
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,839
of shining blue.

65
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:50,040
Go and feel it.

66
00:04:57,040 --> 00:05:00,319
Dad, can you never leave me?

67
00:05:01,439 --> 00:05:02,000
Okay.

68
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,199
I won't leave.

69
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,439
I'll always be with my little baby.

70
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:11,360
Professor Chu, I'm scared.

71
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:13,600
Don't be scared.

72
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,199
I won't let anything happen to you.

73
00:05:22,439 --> 00:05:23,399
Stop following me.

74
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,680
Don't meddle in my business.

75
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,079
Do you think I want to meddle?

76
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:29,360
I didn't expect you to be a daddy's girl.

77
00:05:29,759 --> 00:05:30,879
Jiang Yue, I never considered you

78
00:05:30,879 --> 00:05:32,480
your father as my family.

79
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,399
If it weren't for your intervention,

80
00:05:33,399 --> 00:05:34,680
no one would interfere with my life.

81
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:35,920
I would be better than now.

82
00:05:40,439 --> 00:05:41,639
We are brother and sister.

83
00:05:42,959 --> 00:05:43,720
Forget the rest.

84
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:32,240
Qi, Qi.

85
00:07:30,839 --> 00:07:31,759
It's not a big deal.

86
00:07:32,759 --> 00:07:33,399
Thank you.

87
00:07:42,759 --> 00:07:43,319
You're awake.

88
00:07:44,079 --> 00:07:45,879
[The moment Jiang Yue picked me up,]

89
00:07:46,519 --> 00:07:48,519
all the torn parts came together.

90
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:49,920
Why don't you say anything?

91
00:07:50,759 --> 00:07:51,839
I like you.

92
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:53,560
I'm sure of it.

93
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,000
I like you.

94
00:07:55,199 --> 00:07:56,040
Don't scare me.

95
00:07:58,720 --> 00:07:59,360
I...

96
00:07:59,959 --> 00:08:00,920
I want some water.

97
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:02,439
I'll go get you some.

98
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:23,839
Thank you.

99
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:24,600
I've finished it.

100
00:08:29,519 --> 00:08:30,800
Why do you hurt yourself?

101
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:35,240
Professor Chu

102
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:36,639
wouldn't let me get hurt.

103
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,879
Look, I'm fine.

104
00:08:38,879 --> 00:08:39,840
I'm asking for the reason.

105
00:08:40,679 --> 00:08:41,759
The reason?

106
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,480
How can I tell you?

107
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,679
Competition.

108
00:08:47,159 --> 00:08:47,960
I'm going to participate

109
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:48,960
in a photography competition.

110
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,159
It's just a competition.

111
00:08:50,879 --> 00:08:51,720
Do you have to put yourself

112
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:52,840
in such a dangerous situation?

113
00:08:55,639 --> 00:08:56,399
You know,

114
00:08:56,919 --> 00:08:57,960
there is a kind of experience

115
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:59,720
called near-death experience.

116
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:00,919
Many artists

117
00:09:00,919 --> 00:09:02,480
use this method to find inspiration.

118
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:03,480
I know.

119
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:04,559
And

120
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:07,039
I did find inspiration.

121
00:09:07,639 --> 00:09:09,519
This kind of competition at the cost of life

122
00:09:10,759 --> 00:09:11,440
is not worth it.

123
00:09:12,879 --> 00:09:13,679
But

124
00:09:14,039 --> 00:09:16,080
this is very precious to me.

125
00:09:16,679 --> 00:09:17,960
But you are more precious to me.

126
00:09:22,759 --> 00:09:25,480
I just want to go further

127
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,720
in the field of photography.

128
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:30,720
I have been stuck for a long time.

129
00:09:32,399 --> 00:09:34,679
Professor Chu is willing to help me.

130
00:09:35,279 --> 00:09:37,080
Why don't I accept it?

131
00:09:38,159 --> 00:09:40,360
I won't let you see that professor again.

132
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,240
Jiang Yue.

133
00:09:43,759 --> 00:09:44,399
Lie down.

134
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:52,679
Lie down.

135
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:01,279
I've asked for leave from school.

136
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:03,080
Have a good rest.

137
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,399
You didn't imprison Lu Qi, did you?

138
00:11:02,279 --> 00:11:02,879
Mr. Xiaojiang.

139
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:15,879
Is that all you've got?

140
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:28,919
Listen.

141
00:11:29,519 --> 00:11:30,120
if you hurt her again,

142
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:31,519
I'll kill you.

143
00:11:33,759 --> 00:11:34,320
Jiang Yue,

144
00:11:36,759 --> 00:11:38,200
on what ground are you saying this to me?

145
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,399
I'm her brother.

146
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:42,399
Do you believe that?

147
00:11:45,399 --> 00:11:46,399
The new mansion of 3Z

148
00:11:47,559 --> 00:11:49,200
is where the three of us met for the first time.

149
00:11:49,919 --> 00:11:50,799
At that time,

150
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,639
all I could feel

151
00:11:52,639 --> 00:11:53,759
was your hostility towards me.

152
00:12:01,159 --> 00:12:01,799
Later,

153
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:03,600
it was that rainy night.

154
00:12:04,159 --> 00:12:06,039
If you like getting wet, do it yourself.

155
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:07,200
Come home with me.

156
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:08,080
Jiang Yue.

157
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:11,960
From treating me as a sister to a woman,

158
00:12:13,639 --> 00:12:14,399
Mr. Xiaojiang,

159
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:16,679
did this change

160
00:12:16,679 --> 00:12:18,080
start from that time?

161
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:20,879
Or

162
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:23,279
the beach?

163
00:12:23,879 --> 00:12:25,279
I have a house nearby,

164
00:12:25,559 --> 00:12:26,639
at 13 Beach Road.

165
00:12:27,039 --> 00:12:27,840
You can come to see me.

166
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:35,519
What did you do to her

167
00:12:35,519 --> 00:12:36,639
after you took her away?

168
00:12:42,639 --> 00:12:43,639
I'll emphasize again,

169
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:46,440
don't get close to her.

170
00:12:46,879 --> 00:12:47,639
You like her?

171
00:12:47,639 --> 00:12:48,240
Yes.

172
00:12:48,639 --> 00:12:50,320
Is it the kind of love between a man and a woman?

173
00:12:58,639 --> 00:12:59,960
Do you know what love is?

174
00:13:03,039 --> 00:13:03,840
Jiang Yue,

175
00:13:05,159 --> 00:13:06,879
a vice president of 3Z in name only,

176
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:08,200
should live a very easy life.

177
00:13:09,759 --> 00:13:10,559
But in fact,

178
00:13:11,639 --> 00:13:12,480
the heavy burden on your shoulders

179
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:14,159
makes it hard for you to move an inch.

180
00:13:14,559 --> 00:13:16,200
Not to mention the fierce competition.

181
00:13:16,679 --> 00:13:17,679
Do you like Lu Qi

182
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:19,720
with such a Jiang Yue?

183
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:24,440
Can you afford to like her?

184
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,440
Is she your kind?

185
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:30,480
It's none of your business.

186
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:32,440
Don't you want to know

187
00:13:33,679 --> 00:13:35,200
why Lu Qi always comes to me?

188
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,919
She's always treated you as her brother,

189
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:41,440
but you changed your mind.

190
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,840
So she can only passively accept it

191
00:13:45,879 --> 00:13:46,879
and silently bear it.

192
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,480
Finally, she can't bear it anymore,

193
00:13:48,759 --> 00:13:49,440
so she came to me.

194
00:13:52,679 --> 00:13:53,960
I just helped her get out of it.

195
00:14:00,679 --> 00:14:01,519
You should thank me.

196
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:07,440
Don't get close to her again.

197
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:09,440
Or I'll kill you.

198
00:14:26,879 --> 00:14:28,720
How is Professor Chu?

199
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:38,080
Professor Chu, I'm so sorry.

200
00:14:38,720 --> 00:14:40,080
I'll treat you to dinner later.

201
00:15:35,759 --> 00:15:36,960
How is it going now?

202
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:38,759
The prey has taken the bait.

203
00:15:39,559 --> 00:15:40,120
Prey?

204
00:15:41,440 --> 00:15:42,879
Did you get Gao Qiao?

205
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:46,919
Gao Qiao is Jiang Changfa's confidant.

206
00:15:49,159 --> 00:15:50,720
He's much better than his son

207
00:15:50,720 --> 00:15:51,639
who only delivers goods.

208
00:15:52,919 --> 00:15:54,039
If we get Gao Qiao,

209
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:58,679
the destruction of 3Z Group will be around the corner.

210
00:16:02,080 --> 00:16:02,679
Butterfly.

211
00:16:05,639 --> 00:16:07,360
Over the years, 3Z Group

212
00:16:07,799 --> 00:16:09,240
has monopolized the old artists

213
00:16:10,279 --> 00:16:12,240
and even reached out to the young.

214
00:16:13,759 --> 00:16:16,000
Even Lin Chuanye, whom we have painstakingly negotiated,

215
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:18,000
was poached by them.

216
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:21,360
They left no way out for others.

217
00:16:22,159 --> 00:16:23,679
Lin Chuanye, an international master,

218
00:16:24,559 --> 00:16:26,919
his dark imagery style

219
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:30,480
is indeed popular among the young.

220
00:16:32,159 --> 00:16:33,440
If you help me sabotage this exhibition,

221
00:16:34,440 --> 00:16:36,960
I'll give you whatever you want.

222
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:39,240
I don't take just any job.
